From ba11c898f6d5082c3e2d0e92f8a6ecd8e8134849 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: BeneSys Fix <fix@benesys.in>
Date: Fri, 20 Mar 2026 10:37:36 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: Import/Export Excel for Items and Parties master pages

Frontend (client/src/components/ImportExport.tsx):
- Export button: downloads all records as formatted .xlsx
- Import button: upload Excel/CSV to bulk create or update records
- Template button: downloads blank template with sample data
- Import result dialog: shows created/updated counts and any errors
- Uses SheetJS (already in package.json) - no new dependency

Backend (server/routes.ts):
- GET /api/items/export - returns items as JSON for Excel
- POST /api/items/import - bulk create/update items from Excel rows
- GET /api/parties/export - returns parties as JSON for Excel
- POST /api/parties/import - bulk create/update parties from Excel rows
- Smart upsert: if Code matches existing record, updates it; else creates new

Storage (server/storage.ts):
- Added getItemByCode(code, companyId) for import deduplication
- Added getPartyByCode(code, companyId) for import deduplication

Pages:
- items.tsx: ImportExport component added next to Add Item button
- parties.tsx: ImportExport component added next to Add Customer button
